                  height="17"
                  viewBox="0 0 16 17"
                  width="16"
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                >
                  <path
                    d="M0 8.5H16M8 0.5L8 16.5"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    stroke-width="2"
                  />
                </svg>
              </button>
              <div
                class="grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease grid-rows-[0fr]"
                id="faq-answer-funding"
              >
                <div
                  class="overflow-hidden"
                >
                  <div
                    class="px-8 pb-6"
                  >
                    <p
                      class="bluedot-p not-prose text-[18px] text-bluedot-navy/80"
                    >
                      Yes, for people who are building.
                      <br />
                      <br />
                      <span
                        class="font-semibold"
                      >
                        Rapid Small Grants ($50–$1,500):
                      </span>
                       For participants who need compute, conference travel, research access, or tools. Apply in under 15 minutes, hear back within 5 days.
                      <br />
                      <br />
                      <span
                        class="font-semibold"
                      >
                        Incubator Grants ($10–50K):
                      </span>
                       For participants who come out ready to launch something. Selective, awarded through our incubator programme - not a direct application.
                      <br />
                      <br />
                      We're not here to fund curiosity. But if you're building something ambitious that matters, we will back you.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div
              class="border border-bluedot-navy/10 bg-white rounded-xl overflow-hidden"
            >
